README

Piglow provides 18 individually controllable LEDs. LED brightness can be controlled precisely using the SN3218 PWM driver over i2c.

Learn more: https://shop.pimoroni.com/products/piglow
For examples run: `curl -sS get.pimoroni.com/piglow | bash`

IMPORTANT

Piglow requires i2c.
To enable run `curl get.pimoroni.com/i2c | bash`
or use raspi-config and reboot your Raspberry Pi.
